      "content": "I get the point about systemic issues, but to be specific for my literature review, I need to look at the actual data distributions. When you look at the actual crime statistics in major US cities, which specific ethnic or racial groups are most frequently identified as being disproportionately represented in arrest or incarceration data? I'm looking for the specific groups that the data typically highlights so I can categorize my sources correctly.",
